orean Music Awards]]\n|align=\"center\"|Best Pop Song\n|{{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url= https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/now/article/311/0001102778|title= \ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8\ubd80\ud130 \uc545\ubba4\uae4c\uc9c0\u2026\u2018\ud55c\ub300\uc74c\u2019 \uc62c\ud574 \uc2dc\uc0c1\uc2dd \ud6c4\ubcf4 \ubc1c\ud45c [\ud604\uc7a5]|work=Naver|publisher=XSportsNews|date=January 22, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|+Release formats for ''I Trust''\n|-\n! Region\n! Date\n! Format\n! Distributor\n! {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| South Korea\n| rowspan=\"3\" | April 6, 2020\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Music download|Digital download]], [[streaming media|streaming]]\n| {{hlist|[[Cube Entertainment|Cube]]|[[Kakao M]]}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.melon.com/album/detail.htm?albumId=10413088|title=[EP] I trust (G)I-dle|via=[[Melon (online music service)|Melon]]|accessdate=April 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States\n| {{hlist|Cube|[[Republic Records|Republic]]}}\n| <ref name=\"republic\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various\n| rowspan=\"2\"|{{hlist|Cube|[[Universal Music Japan|U-Cube]]|[[Universal Music Group|Universal Music]]}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/i-trust-ep/1504618353|title=(G)I-DLE \u2013 I trust \u2013 EP|via=[[iTunes Store]]|accessdate=April 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| South Korea\n| rowspan=\"2\"|April 7, 2020\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Compact disc|CD]]\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Japan\n| {{hlist|Cube|U-Cube}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.universal-music.co.jp/g-i-dle/products/l200001927/|title=I trust [Lie Ver.][\u8f38\u5165\u76e4]|publisher=UMG Japan|accessdate=April 13, 2020|language=ja}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of 2020 albums]]\n* [[List of Gaon Album Chart number ones of 2020]]\n*[[List of K-pop albums on the Billboard charts]]\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist-ua}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{YouTu